<p>Use this page to manage your <b>Comments</b>. Your <b>Comments</b> related to different <b>Entries</b> and <b>Manuscript Records</b> appear in the queue below in reverse chronological order by default. Use the search box to locate a specific <b>Manuscript Record</b>.</p>
<p>The <b>Options</b> displayed in the far left column allow you to <b class='btn btn-xs btn-success'>Edit</b> your <b>Comment(s)</b> or <b class='btn btn-xs btn-danger'>Delete</b> your <b>Comment(s)</b> from the selected record.</p>